{"tid":2042622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【調查報導】打壓維吾爾人之中國公司遭美國制裁，但措施存在大量漏洞","createTime":"2020-05-30T02:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T03:19:20.000Z","uid":138409,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"48f92623f90f2af13b7eade510692889e88b3ad5","tid":2042622,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:29:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.icij.org/investigations/china-cables/us-blacklists-chinese-companies-linked-to-uighur-abuses/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icij.org%2Finvestigations%2Fchina-cables%2Fus-blacklists-chinese-companies-linked-to-uighur-abuses%2F&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=9ca35921\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.icij.org/investigations/china-cables/us-blacklists-chinese-companies-linked-to-uighur-abuses/</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手retweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ICIJorg/status/1266365932638810112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FICIJorg%2Fstatus%2F1266365932638810112&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=dad05f6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FICIJorg%2Fstatus%2F1266365932638810112&h=40cc0a57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ICIJorg/status/1266365932638810112</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重點：</span></span><br />\n- 美國商務部日前擴大制裁範圍，涵蓋額外9間中國機構；制裁範圍目前包含33間中國企業及大學<br />\n<br />\n- 制裁黑名單上未針對第三方售貨平台；部分被制裁嘅公司產品依然於美國有售；亞馬遜自己就曾經響武漢肺炎爆發期間，向<span style=\"color: gold;\">浙江大華</span>技術（另一間因新疆監控而被制裁嘅公司） 購買量體溫嘅鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n- Sony同埋Sharp都有提供零部件畀黑名單上面嘅公司，例如<span style=\"color: gold;\">海康威視</span>（即係全球最大監控鏡頭生產商）<br />\n<br />\n- 海康威視 同 浙江大華嘅商品依然響亞馬遜有售<br />\n<br />\n- 有部分響制裁和名單上面嘅中國監控技術公司，用佢哋旗下嘅美國分部身分參加拉斯維加斯嘅工業展，向其他國家推廣佢哋嘅產品（不過個conference最尾因武漢肺炎取消左）<br />\n<br />\n- 亞馬遜同埋微軟都有份提供網絡服務畀至少8間目前受檢視嘅中國監控技術公司<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">延伸閱讀：</span></span><br />\n地鐵砲台山站使用比新疆人權報告被制裁嘅海康威視cctv<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1645752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1645752</a><br />\n<br />\n[突發大獲] 美國blacklist左海康威視<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1636789\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1636789</a>"},{"pid":"f7ea903d4cdf760476196fbbea0a419abb2242de","tid":2042622,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:30:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1008ae8de1d74447fa8f423981e9f3bdd8ce3a43","tid":2042622,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:33:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"286c201b42009e558ab9e3fca2a14b0faa08c2eb","tid":2042622,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:35:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ea9428314e21f8a6f82c489856caaae92149a8d3","tid":2042622,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:35:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb11e977b066112006cfb76a7b945a702503656a","tid":2042622,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:36:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3fdc731f0362ca555a25abb9c8cb6081450cb8e5","tid":2042622,"uid":74783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"216f1593e10f723d3837ba8b25135eb52e4865ab","tid":2042622,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5efcc39e150a46801663a5c9ceae7d243c9dcc49","tid":2042622,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:38:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a95bbd5212f1bec196f8ec5779a93fdd8786b3f6","tid":2042622,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,